<img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1810/465005.png" alt="Finalists in the Assegai Awards 2018 have been announced" width="500" height="190">Visit: http://www.assegaiawards.co.za/2018-award-finalists/ to view our 2018 finalists.This year judging took place over three days to ensure that the awards continue to recognise the innovation and creativity of our local marketers.The announcements are for those campaigns that made it into the top half of all campaigns received. The winners from these campaigns will be announced at our gala evening on Thursday, 8 November 2018.Congratulations to all our finalists.The Assegai Awards gala evening takes place on Thursday, 8 November 2018 at the POLO Room in Inanda, make sure you book your ticket here: http://www.assegaiawards.co.za/awards-evening/